<section id="review" class="container-full section-space">
  <div data-reveal class="reveal-sequence max-w-prose">
    <p class="label">The review</p>
    <h2 class="mt-2 text-section-title text-balance">What the review examines</h2>
    <p class="mt-5 text-[0.9375rem] leading-[1.65] text-muted md:text-base md:leading-[1.65]">
      The review examines the operating conditions that determine whether an AI initiative can create
      value.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-8 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
    <article data-reveal data-reveal-delay="1" class="reveal-sequence panel p-7">
      <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl">Existing expenditure</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 text-[0.9375rem] leading-[1.65] text-muted md:text-base">
        Tools, licences, pilots, implementation fees, internal time and ongoing operating costs.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article data-reveal data-reveal-delay="2" class="reveal-sequence panel p-7">
      <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl">Workflow reality</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 text-[0.9375rem] leading-[1.65] text-muted md:text-base">
        How work is actually performed, where AI is used, what remains manual and where output must
        be checked or reworked.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article data-reveal data-reveal-delay="1" class="reveal-sequence panel p-7">
      <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl">Adoption</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 text-[0.9375rem] leading-[1.65] text-muted md:text-base">
        Who uses the system, how consistently they use it and what prevents wider or more effective
        use.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article data-reveal data-reveal-delay="2" class="reveal-sequence panel p-7">
      <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl">Data and integration</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 text-[0.9375rem] leading-[1.65] text-muted md:text-base">
        Whether source information is accessible, reliable and connected to the systems employees
        already use.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article data-reveal data-reveal-delay="1" class="reveal-sequence panel p-7">
      <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl">Operational value</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 text-[0.9375rem] leading-[1.65] text-muted md:text-base">
        Whether the initiative changes turnaround time, capacity, cost, conversion, quality, margin
        or risk.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article data-reveal data-reveal-delay="2" class="reveal-sequence panel p-7">
      <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl">Decision quality</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 text-[0.9375rem] leading-[1.65] text-muted md:text-base">
        Whether the business should stop, repair, consolidate or expand each initiative.
      </p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>
